</section>
<section class="references" id="sect-00003">
      <title>References</title>
<para id="para-00005">Aach, M, Cruciger, O, Sczesny-Kaiser, M, Hoffken, O, Meindl, R.Ch., Tegenthoff, M, Schwenkreis, P, Sankai, Y, and Schildhaur, TA (2014) Voluntary driven exoskeleton as a new tool for rehabilitation in chronic spinal cord injury: a pilot study. <emphasis effect="italics">The Spine Journal 14</emphasis>(12), 2847-2853. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.spinee.2014.03.042</para>
