<para id="para-00042">Hunt CC (1990) Mammalian muscle spindle: peripheral mechanisms. <emphasis effect="italics">Physiological Reviews 70</emphasis>(3): 643-663. https://doi.org/10.1152/physrev.1990.70.3.643</para>
